messages.subject: I'm still standing tall
messages.msgSnippet: Unschoolers Join me each and everyone of you by responding to this post on the unschooling list. No fowards please. In Subject line write:    Standing/and the
messages.messageBody:
Unschoolers
Join me each and everyone of you by responding to this post on the
unschooling list. No fowards please.

In Subject line write: Standing/and the name of your state.
In the body, just include your first name.


We unite in refusing to let current events take away our strength, even though
we are scared, stressed, and numb.

Even though our hearts are breaking for the loved ones lost, we will remain
committed to take that kind of love and demonstrate it over and over again
for the rest of our lives.

We will stand strong as back up to our families who are and may be put
on active duty. You will not be alone.

We refuse to have innocense taken from our children. We will impower
our children and uplift them daily and continuously teach them to love.

We were down, but now we are standing tall, better than we ever have.


[Non-text portions of this message have been removed]
